snippet.title: Life of Johnny Depp from Childhood to Amber heard
snippet.description:
With ten Golden Globe and three Academy Awards nominations under his belt, Johnny Depp is among the few great actors who chose roles they found interesting, rather than those to succeed at the box office. The captain jack sparrow is one good example that everyone thought was a disaster but collectively grossed over US$ 5 billion. However lately the actor has been surrounded in lots of controversy regarding the relationship with ex-wife amber heard. So Whats lead him to this moment let’s have a look shall we.
